1
00:00:00,760 --> 00:00:01,760
Ateş.

2
00:00:02,400 --> 00:00:03,680
I heard a gunshot.

3
00:00:03,960 --> 00:00:04,480
Ateş.

4
00:00:04,720 --> 00:00:06,560
Son, we heard a gunshot. Are you okay?

5
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:08,680
What did you do to my daughter?

6
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:10,480
There is no need to worry, mom.

7
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:11,640
I am fine.

8
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:13,240
I was cleaning the gun.

9
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,240
It went off suddenly.

10
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:18,840
I am not stupid.

11
00:00:19,360 --> 00:00:21,640
Ateş would not accidentally fire a gun.

12
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:26,639
Why do you interfere in
everything that does not concern you?

13
00:00:26,640 --> 00:00:29,880
Your special interest in Ateş.

14
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,600
What is it to you?

15
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:33,320
I will ask you one last time.

16
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:35,080
Is what Ateş said true?

17
00:00:35,360 --> 00:00:37,240
You could not have hurt those children.

18
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:39,680
They stayed here, but we took care of them.

19
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:40,840
Ateş is lying.

20
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:43,280
They came to prepare our end.

21
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,280
Everything is planned. You see it.

22
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:47,680
First they killed your
brother. Now it is my turn.

23
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:52,240
You tried to kill the woman I love.

24
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:55,200
Now that my partnership is
over, I have nothing left to hide.

25
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:57,480
Nezir?

26
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:00,720
You stand here today thanks to
the belts that struck your back.

27
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:02,920
Who were you?

28
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:03,480
What were you to me?

29
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,960
Why should I have taken
care of you and your sibling?

30
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:07,880
Should I have fed you at my table?

31
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:12,080
I showed you too much mercy.

32
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:18,240
The belt was not enough.
I should have crippled you.

33
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:29,120
I heard what kind of monster
you are, from your own mouth.

34
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,039
My daughter, there are
things you do not know.

35
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:33,360
Do not touch me. Do not
ever call me my daughter.

36
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,959
Can justify the cruelty you
inflicted on Eylül and Tahir,

37
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:39,040
the torture, the murder you committed.

38
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,736
Say the word and I will
deal with that bandit.

39
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,760
Look, Nezir.

40
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:43,920
I warn you again.

41
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,240
Do not come to me with this.

42
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:49,680
If you harm Ateş, you will face me.

43
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,840
Mercan had kidney disease.

44
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,920
She was the only compatible donor.

45
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:58,320
For Mercan to live, Eylül had to die.

46
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,840
Tell me, Ateş.

47
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:04,000
To save the one you love,
would you take another life?

48
